profile_summary:
Kiran Johns is a highly skilled software developer with expertise in systems programming languages, including Rust and C. With a strong foundation in computer science and a passion for building high-quality software, Kiran has established a reputation as a reliable and innovative technologist. Over the course of his career, he has developed a unique blend of technical skills and product knowledge, positioning him as a valuable asset to cutting-edge software development teams.

As an active open-source developer with a portfolio of 157 public repositories, Kiran has consistently demonstrated his technical prowess and commitment to collaboration and knowledge-sharing within the developer community. With a network of 162 followers and a growing reputation as a trusted technical authority, Kiran is well-equipped to drive software development initiatives that require precision, creativity, and a strong understanding of systems programming.
